Code preview of the table CON_合同类型字典表

drop table "CON_ContractTypeCode" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_ContractTypeCode" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_ContractTypeCode"
(
"ContractTypeID" INTEGER not null,
"ContractTypeCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ContractTypeName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"OrderNum" INTEGER not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"BoothConTypeID" INTEGER not null,
constraint PK_CON_CONTRACTTYPECODE primary key ("ContractTypeID")
);

comment on column "CON_ContractTypeCode"."ContractTypeCode" is
'1:展位租赁合同 2:广告位协议';

comment on column "CON_ContractTypeCode"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0:无效';

comment on column "CON_ContractTypeCode"."BoothConTypeID" is
'1:标准与非标展位合同
2:广告位合同';
